Sony's Stringer Says India to Become One of Company's Five Biggest Regions

-- B y   K e t a k i   G o k h a l e
-- 
2011-03-04T07:33:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-04/sony-s-stringer-says-india-to-become-one-of-company-s-five-biggest-regions.html
  Sony Corp. (6758)  Chief Executive Officer
Howard Stringer said  India  will “shortly” become one of the
company’s top five regions for sales.  Stringer was speaking in Goregaon, a Mumbai suburb.  To contact the reporter on this story:
